metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Walk Like An Egyptian has complexity on par with the typical song, having near-average scores in Chord Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody and below-average scores in Melodic Complexity.
key_conclusion: Walk Like An Egyptian has sections analyzed in the following keys: B Mixolydian,  and B Dorian.  Click on the linked cheat sheets for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: The prechorus has a subdominant function. Just because the song hangs around at the IV chord for a little bit does not mean the tonic has shifted. In the context of the song, the tonic is still E.
